sql_query.sql: SELECT "user_emails"."id", "user_emails"."user_id", "user_emails"."email", "user_emails"."primary", "user_emails"."created_at", "user_emails"."updated_at" FROM "user_emails" WHERE "user_emails"."user_id" = 1015 AND "user_emails"."primary" = TRUE LIMIT 1

SELECT "users".* FROM "users" INNER JOIN "user_emails" ON "user_emails"."user_id" = "users"."id" WHERE (lower(user_emails.email) IN ('anne941@discourse.org')) AND "users"."admin" = TRUE AND (users.id > 0) ORDER BY "users"."id" ASC LIMIT 1
